title: website: Google Code Archive go default source 404
body:
I'm not really sure if this goes here or in some Google Code | Archive reporter but when I click default source from google code archive I get a 404.  Click this [link](https://code.google.com/archive/p/go/source), then click default: source.  You should get a 404.  I'm guessing it's because you guys moved everything over to github and didn't clean this repo, but i'm just guessing.

update:  all the links 404 on the site
